parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Trailer Frame and Body Attachment
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to secure the trailer body to the frame can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as well as damage to the trailer and other vehicles.
symptoms: Loose or missing bolts attaching the trailer body to the frame
causing the trailer to sway or detach while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Trailer Sway and Loss of Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the trailer, particularly the placement of the fresh water tank and axles, can cause the trailer to sway and lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Trailer swaying or fishtailing while towing
particularly when the fresh water tank is full or when weight is placed at the rear of the trailer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Castle Rock ST tires can cause sudden loss of air pressure, leading to tire blowouts, tread separation, and loss of control, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: bulge or bubble on the tire

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trailer axle can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The tire on the trailer is bent in towards the center
abnormal noises or vibrations while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery mounting system can cause the battery to fall out of the vehicle, leading to electrical shorts, fires, or loss of power, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: battery falls out of the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Improper Trailer Frame Assembly and Fastening
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The improper assembly and fastening of the trailer frame can lead to structural failure, causing the trailer body to detach from the frame while in motion, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: screws or bolts not securing the trailer body to the frame.
